trans-unit.source: Represents an event that an instance store raises to notify hosts about a condition.
trans-unit.target: 代表執行個體存放區會引發以通知主機有條件之資訊的事件。

trans-unit.source: Examples: <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent" /> and <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent" />.
trans-unit.target: 範例：<see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent" /> 和 <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent" />。

trans-unit.source: Compares two instances of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 比較 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件的兩個執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The object to be compared with the current object.
trans-unit.target: 要與目前物件比較的物件。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object and the passed object converted as the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> are the same.
trans-unit.target: 判斷目前的 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件與已轉換成 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 的傳遞物件是否相同。

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這兩個物件相同，則傳回 <see langword="True" />，否則傳回 <see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: The object to be compared with the current object.
trans-unit.target: 要與目前物件比較的物件。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object and the passed <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object are the same.
trans-unit.target: 判斷目前的 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件與傳遞的 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件是否相同。

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這兩個物件相同，則傳回 <see langword="True" />，否則傳回 <see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 執行個體的雜湊程式碼。

trans-unit.source: The hash code for the instance.
trans-unit.target: 此執行個體的雜湊程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Returns the XName (namespace combined with name) of the persistence event.
trans-unit.target: 傳回持續性事件的 XName (與名稱結合的命名空間)。

trans-unit.source: XName of the persistence event
trans-unit.target: 持續性事件的 XName。

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的第一個 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The second <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的第二個 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects are the same.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，這個值會指出指定的 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件是否相同。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the two objects are the same; otherwise, <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這兩個物件相同則為 <see langword="True" />，否則為 <see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的第一個 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The second <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: 要比較的第二個 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects are not the same.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，這個值會指出指定的 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> 物件是否不同。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the two objects are the same; otherwise, <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這兩個物件相同則為 <see langword="True" />，否則為 <see langword="False" />。
